        {
            "header": "Staff of Ice",
            "description": "Collect 3 parts, then defend the Staff.",
            "subsections": [
                {
                    "header": "Part 1 (Monocle)",
                    "description": "Dropped when killing the first Shock Mimic",
                    "elements": [
                        {
                            "pic": {
                                "src": "assets/.jpg",
                                "alt": "Monocle"
                            }
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "header": "Part 2 (Staff)",
                    "description": "Parts 2 and 3 can be collected in any order. Break Aetheric Lanterns in the Tombs until symbols are revealed. When the lantern appears in the correct location, and the Monocle part has been aquired, several symbols will appear on the wall over a mural. Shoot the symbols in ascending order (each symbol represents a Roman Numeral counting from 1 to 8). Finally, kill the creatures emerging from the portals until the part appears by the mural.",
                    "elements": [
                        {
                            "pic": {
                                "src": "assets/.jpg",
                                "alt": "Correct lantern location"
                            }
                        },
                        {
                            "pic": {
                                "src": "assets/.jpg",
                                "alt": "Symbols to shoot in order"
                            }
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "header": "Part 3 (Head Piece)",
                    "description": "Parts 2 and 3 can be collected in any order. Break Aetheric Lanterns in the Neolithic Catacombs until symbols are revealed. When the lantern appears in the correct location, and the Monocle part has been aquired, several symbols will appear on the wall over a mural. Shoot the symbols in ascending order (each symbol represents a Roman Numeral counting from 1 to 10). Finally, kill the creatures emerging from the portals until the part appears by the mural.",
                    "elements": [
                        {
                            "pic": {
                                "src": "assets/.jpg",
                                "alt": "Correct lantern location"
                            }
                        },
                        {
                            "pic": {
                                "src": "assets/.jpg",
                                "alt": "Symbols to shoot in order"
                            }
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "header": "Aquire the Staff",
                    "description": "Activate the Staff of Ice pieces on the Plinth in the Dark Aether. Then, defend the Staff of Ice until it's assembled. If you fail, you can try again the following round. One player may now retrieve the Staff of Ice.",
                    "elements": [
                        {
                            "pic": {
                                "src": "assets/.jpg",
                                "alt": "Location to activate Plinth"
                            }
                        },
                        {
                            "pic": {
                                "src": "assets/.jpg",
                                "alt": "Staff of Ice"
                            }
                        }
                    ]
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "header": "Upgraded Ice Staff (Ull's Arrow)",
            "description": "The upgrade process must be done once, then all players may upgrade their Staff of Ice (TODO).",
            "subsections": [
                {
                    "header": "Quickly Freeze 3 Lanterns",
                    "description": "Freeze 3 Aetheric Lanterns with the Staff of Ice within 10 seconds. A simple strategy involves using a different weapon to shoot the lanterns in the Ossuary and the Shrine of the Hierophants until they're visible through the doors from the Subterranean Temple. Then, shoot the lantern in the Subterranean Temple until it's near one of the doors, such that all 3 are lined up and can be shot quickly in a row. When done successfully, Archibald will speak, and the symbols for the next step will appear.",
                    "elements": [
                        {
                            "pic": {
                                "src": "assets/.jpg",
                                "alt": "Freezing an Aetheric Lantern"
                            }
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "header": "Shoot 3 Runes in the Dark Aether Nexus",
                    "description": "With the Staff of Ice, shoot 3 Runes on the floating rocks in the Dark Aether Sky. After each symbol has been shot, the rock will lower closer to the ground. When all 3 rocks have been lowered, memorize the 3 symbols for the next step. The symbols and locations of the rocks are randomized each game.",
                    "elements": [
                        {
                            "pic": {
                                "src": "assets/.jpg",
                                "alt": "Floating rock with a purple Rune"
                            }
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "header": "Teleport to the Energy",
                    "description": "Exit the Dark Aether Nexus and locate the Gateway that has been closed. The Gateway will be covered in various symbols, including the 3 from the previous step. Use the Staff of Ice to shoot the same Runes on the outside Gateway and enter it. If the wrong symbols were shot, you will appear in the sky and take heavy fall damage. When done successfully, you will appear on a floating rock next to a purple orb. Interact to touch the Energy and begin the next step.",
                    "elements": [
                        {
                            "pic": {
                                "src": "assets/.jpg",
                                "alt": "Closed Gateway with Runes"
                            }
                        },
                        {
                            "pic": {
                                "src": "assets/.jpg",
                                "alt": "Floating rock with Energy"
                            }
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "header": "Feed the Energy",
                    "description": "The purple orb will slowly move around the Dark Aether Nexus and can be fed by killing enemies. Stay close to the Energy as it moves around the Dark Aether. All players should stay as close to the Energy as possible and constantly killing enemies, or the step will fail. If the step fails, you must repeat the previous step to teleport to the Energy. If the Energy reaches the Plinth, the step will be completed.",
                    "elements": [
                        {
                            "pic": {
                                "src": "assets/.jpg",
                                "alt": "Killing enemies while following the Energy"
                            }
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "header": "Touch the Staff to the Altar",
                    "description": "Interact on the glowing purple energy to upgrade the Staff of Ice into the Ull's Arrow.",
                    "elements": [
                        {
                            "pic": {
                                "src": "assets/.jpg",
                                "alt": "Location to upgrade Staff of Ice"
                            }
                        }
                    ]
                }
            ]
        },
