                {
                    "header": "5. Boss Fight",
                    "description": "You cannot leave the boss fight until it's done. Make sure you have perks, armor, strong weapons, and anything else you want to bring.",
                    "elements": [
                        {
                            "full": true,
                            "step": {
                                "title": "Activate the pedestal",
                                "description": "Interact on the pedestal in the Dark Aether Nexus to open the bridge to the boss fight arena. Then, interact on the Sentinel Artifact to start the Final Encounter."
                            }
                        },
                        {
                            "pic": {
                                "src": "assets/.jpg",
                                "alt": "Pedestal to open the bridge"
                            }
                        },
                        {
                            "pic": {
                                "src": "assets/.jpg",
                                "alt": "Sentinel Artifact to start boss fight"
                            }
                        },
                        {
                            "full": true,
                            "step": {
                                "title": "Phase 1",
                                "description": "The Sentinel Artifact has 9 health stages that must be depleted to win the fight, and 1 health stage will be lost each time a Sentinel Artifact is shattered. The artifact will start by rotating in a circle and shooting a deadly laser. It will also slowly move up and down to hit both levels of the arena. Eventually, it will turn purple for a short period of time, where it can be damaged (this will not be indicated on the boss bar until it is shattered). Each time an artifact is shattered, another one will join the artifact to spin around with an additional laser. All of the artifacts will turn purple at the same time, and it is possible to shatter multiple artifacts during this time to reduce multiple health stages. After the 4th artifact has been shattered, the fight will continue to Phase 2."
                            }
                        },
                        {
                            "pic": {
                                "src": "assets/.jpg",
                                "alt": "Spinning Sentinel Artifact"
                            }
                        },
                        {
                            "pic": {
                                "src": "assets/.jpg",
                                "alt": "Shooting the artifact when it glows purple"
                            }
                        },
                        {
                            "pic": {
                                "src": "assets/.jpg",
                                "alt": "Shattered artifact"
                            }
                        },
                        {
                            "pic": {
                                "src": "assets/.jpg",
                                "alt": "Multiple spinning artifacts"
                            }
                        },
                        {
                            "full": true,
                            "step": {
                                "title": "Phase 2",
                                "description": "During this phase, the 4 previously shattered artifacts will remain spinning and shooting lasers, but can no longer be shattered. The next 4 artifacts must be shattered one at a time, and will spawn attached to an enemy. Kill the enemy holding the artifact, then quickly shatter the artifact before it goes away. If the artifact vanishes before it's shattered, it will respawn on a new enemy. The artifact will be carried by a Heavy Zombie, Doppelghast, Shock Mimic, and Amalgam. After these 4 artifacts have been shattered, the fight will continue to the final phase."
                            }
                        },
                        {
                            "pic": {
                                "src": "assets/.jpg",
                                "alt": "TODO empowered by the Sentinel Artifact"
                            }
                        },
                        {
                            "pic": {
                                "src": "assets/.jpg",
                                "alt": "Artifact to shatter after being dropped"
                            }
                        },
                        {
                            "full": true,
                            "step": {
                                "title": "Phase 3",
                                "description": "For the final phase, the 8 previously shattered artifacts will all shoot a laser at the 9th and final artifact. After a brief animation, the final artifact will float up to a wall where it can be shattered. Finish off the Sentinel Artifact before it destroys you. If it isn't shattered quick enough, the game will end. When done successfully, the artifact will float down to the center of the arena, where it can be picked up."
                            }
                        },
                        {
                            "pic": {
                                "src": "assets/.jpg",
                                "alt": "Final artifact being powered by the first 8"
                            }
                        },
                        {
                            "pic": {
                                "src": "assets/.jpg",
                                "alt": "Shattering the final artifact"
                            }
                        },
                        {
                            "full": true,
                            "step": {
                                "title": "Retrieve the Sentinel Artifact",
                                "description": "Interact on the Sentinel Artifact to complete the main quest and play a cutscene."
                            }
                        },
                        {
                            "pic": {
                                "src": "assets/.jpg",
                                "alt": "Sentinel Artifact"
                            }
                        }
